EXTRACT I am fascinated by media references hinting that the prosecution's case against Duduzane was strengthened following a conversation with Fana Hlongwane, the arms deal-connected businessman, who was present when Ajay Gupta is alleged to have offered Jonas the bribe. Duduzane was in the room too, and if he is vulnerable to prosecution on that basis, then so is Hlongwane. We'll undoubtedly hear more about this. Others may want to contemplate who else was in the room when they cut their own corrupt deals. A subscription helps you enjoy the best of our business content every day along with benefits such as exclusive Financial Times articles, Morningstar financial data, and digital access to the Sunday Times and Times Select. **Promotion: 
